alert.note: Alert for Dukes (Massachusetts) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: Coastal Flood Warning issued January 09 at 6:55PM EST until January 10 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Boston
info.description: ...COASTAL FLOOD WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM TO 10 AM EST WEDNESDAY... * WHAT...One to two feet of inundation above ground level expected in low-lying areas near shorelines and tidal waterways (4.0 to 5.1 feet Mean Lower Low Water). * WHERE...Dukes MA County. * WHEN...From 6 AM to 10 AM EST Wednesday. * IMPACTS...Numerous roads may be closed. Low lying property including homes, businesses, and some critical infrastructure will be inundated. Some shoreline erosion will occur. && Time of high total tides are approximate to the nearest hour.
